These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: martial-arts, fantasy, crime
3 different pets are kept: turtle, hedgehog, fish
1. the owner of the fish is somewhere between the person watching martial-arts movies and the owner of the hedgehog##7
2. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##5
3. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3   |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | fantasy | martial-arts |
| Pet           | hedgehog  | fish     | turtle  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, soul, folk
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, bus, roller
1. the person driving the motorbike is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of pop is somewhere between the fan of folk and the person driving the bus##7
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | soul | pop | folk |
| Transport     | bus       | roller     | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, almond-milk, cola
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, car, snowmobile
1. the person driving the car is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person driving the ship##7
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |   3    |
| Beverage    | iced-tea | almond-milk | cola  |
| Transport   | snowmobile  | car  | ship |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, accountant, social-worker
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, crime, musical
1. the bartender is somewhere between the person watching musical movies and the accountant##7
2. the person watching crime movies is not the bartender##6
3. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching crime movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |      3      |
| Job           | accountant | bartender | social-worker     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime    | spy          | musical |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-5::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, pop, electronic
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, trike, boat
1. the person driving the trike is somewhere between the person driving the boat and the fan of pop##7
2. the person driving the train is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
3. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | ambient      | electronic     | pop   |
| Transport     | boat | trike | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-6::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep, country
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, polish, american
1. the argentine is on the left or right of the polish##3
2. the polish is somewhere to the left of the argentine##5
3. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the american##1
4. the fan of dubstep is somewhere between the american and the fan of ambient##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | country    | dubstep     | ambient     |
| Nationality   | american | polish | argentine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-7::.
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, horse, ferret
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, rowing, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere between the owner of the hedgehog and the person who's sport is tennis##7
3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Pet     | ferret       | horse      | hedgehog       |
| Sport   | tennis | volleyball | rowing |

