2. the person watching satire movies is somewhere between the person watching zombie movies and the accountant##7
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Job           | architect | analyst  | accountant |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie      | satire | comedy      |

