.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, card-games, video-games
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, designer, scientist
1. the scientist is not the person who's hobby is video-games##6
2. the designer is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
3. the dressmaker is somewhere between the designer and the person who's hobby is card-games##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | card-games | video-games | puzzles   |
| Job     | scientist    | dressmaker  | designer |

