.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, fanta, lemonade
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, rugby, volleyball
1. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere between the person drinking fanta and the person who's sport is rugby##7

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | fanta   | lemonade    | water |
| Sport      | volleyball | basketball | rugby |

