2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
3. the mexican is not the person who's hobby is reading##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Hobby         | reading | writing | gardening |
| Nationality   | polish    | indonesian    | mexican         |

