.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-12::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, broccoli, orange
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, martial-arts, mystery
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching satire movies is somewhere between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person eating cauliflower##7
3. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the right of the person watching satire movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Food          | cauliflower  | orange       | broccoli     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | satire | martial-arts |

