2. the person eating carrot is the person eating carrot##1
3. the person eating cabbage is somewhere between the turkish and the egyptian##7
4. the egyptian is the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | carrot | cabbage     | kale   |
| Nationality   | turkish   | german | egyptian |

