.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, hot-chocolate, milk
The people have 3 different jobs:  freelancer, librarian, security-guard
1. the person drinking water is on the right of the freelancer##1
2. the person drinking milk is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the librarian##7
3. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the librarian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate      | milk     | water |
| Job        | security-guard | freelancer | librarian    |

 